previous.message: The training is nothing! Will is everything!
previous.author: batman

current.message: People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy and I can’t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man, I’m flesh and blood, I can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol… as a symbol I can be incorruptible, I can be everlasting.
current.author: batman

next.message: It’s not who you are underneath, it’s what you do that defines you.
next.author: batman
